{
  "stem": "21786.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I did the wash, for instance, for the SS men that are responsible for the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he gave me the potato peelings and the guys knew that I will be getting it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they did something like you can buy nowadays, and we baked them on the top of this stove.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had around me about 15 guys whom-- who belonged to our group, whom I was feeding this way.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, when we got something or we organized something, we always divided it into this group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Roden, you had explained to us about the food rations in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was it any different in Schwarzheide?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a little better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a little better in the sense that the bread was-- we-- we got, I don't know-- I don't want to exaggerate-- but something like between 100 and 150 grams of bread.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we got the soup in the factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It had really potatoes in it and-- and some kind of meat, probably.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, horse meat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it doesn't make any diff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were getting a-- a ration of margarine and we were getting a small ration of ersatz marmalade.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had-- and it was about-- the estimate was about 800 to 1,000 calories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One couldn't naturally work and survive it a long time unless one tried to organize something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like when people were working in the factory, they got something, somewhere, through the civilian workers who took mercy and misery.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Also there were French and British prisoners who made sure that the guys will get something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Also we always did something to keep their attention and to be a little bit more merciful.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
